 factory before all the failsafes have collapsed?</p>\n\n<p><em><strong>Cyberion</strong></em> is a game of hand-management, and you must use your robot cards wisely, either to repair the machine cards or to trigger powerful effects. The machines get harder to repair throughout the game, but you'll also have opportunities to increase the magnitude of the effects your robot can trigger.</p>\n\n<p><em>&mdash;description from the designer</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<span class='text-muted'>This page does not exist. You can edit this page to create it.</span>","website":{"url":"https://inpatience.com/en/Our_Games-26-Cyberion","title":"Cyberion Website"},"imageid":"7610938","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__small/img/iCFg2Rb67x7Jk7joWnW_UazCyrA=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic7610938.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__micro/img/U45XKmXiPpqJEEhpnYHrBkkP0v0=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic7610938.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__square/img/3dBsBjquKnHY7gbYQeqtOND9ZxU=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic7610938.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__tallthumb/img/Ytg2LuqngGBf-F5rlSxjqiY8A9g=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic7610938.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__previewthumb/img/uCGiz2xL6GpHmC8L2bE1rJZoxgw=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic7610938.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__square200/img/rlb-eemueE_WZYKcsmMA8mQt-uA=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic7610938.jpg","original":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__original/img/nHi_g-6XLSuDei4TCMUL38N0VNo=/0x0/filters:format(jpeg)/pic7610938.jpg"},"imagepagehref":"/image/7610938/cyberion","imageurl":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/vr9ebyrLGquq79V_mUjd8w__itemrep/img/ZJtiu3kPW-niQKcasD8jEtg0D1c=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic7610938.jpg","imageurl@2x":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/